Invocation Name: chums up
des:
Fan made homage to recreate that epic moment from World of Warcraft history in Upper Blackrock Spire with Pals for Life. By saying "Alexa, ask chums up, let's do this" she will promptly respond with the classic battle cry of "Leeroy Jenkins!". 32.33% (repeating of course) of the time Alexa will add a little something special afterwards.

Skill does not require any additional hardware or software.
Skill is not sponsored or endorsed by Blizzard Entertainment, Inc in any way.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
